---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Become a Guardian" description="Adams Farm's guardian model — our breeding dogs live in loving family homes, not a kennel.">
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow">Get Involved</p>
      <h1>Become a Guardian</h1>
      <p class="page-intro">Give one of our breeding dogs a loving, permanent home — and we handle the rest.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="section page-section">
    <div class="container prose-narrow">
      <p>Adams Farm&rsquo;s breeding dogs don&rsquo;t live in a kennel. They live as members of a family &mdash; in loving homes, with people who care for them every day, while remaining part of our breeding program.</p>

      <p>This is what makes the guardian model different: our dogs get to be dogs. They&rsquo;re loved, socialized, and part of daily life, not confined to a breeding facility. In return, guardian families give our program something a kennel never could &mdash; a dog raised the same way your puppy will be.</p>

      <p>Here&rsquo;s the idea in plain terms: a guardian family provides the everyday home &mdash; the walks, the couch, the belly rubs &mdash; and the dog lives with them full-time as a family pet. Adams Farm handles what&rsquo;s needed for the dog&rsquo;s role in the breeding program, and the dog only comes back to us briefly, for breeding or whelping, before returning home to its family.</p>

      <p>Puppies are whelped in the Campbell home, where Douglas and Erika oversee everything from birth through early development. But the sires and dams themselves &mdash; the dogs who make each litter possible &mdash; live their lives in the homes of families who love them.</p>

      <p class="prose-emphasis">It&rsquo;s a simple idea: dogs raised in love make better companions. That&rsquo;s true for our breeding dogs, and it&rsquo;s true for the puppies they bring into the world.</p>

      <p>Every guardianship is a little different, and the specifics &mdash; what&rsquo;s involved, how it works, and what to expect &mdash; are things we walk through personally with each family. If the idea appeals to you, the best next step is simply to reach out and talk with us directly.</p>

      <div class="page-cta">
        <a href="tel:+13363388660" class="btn btn-primary">Call 336-338-8660</a>
        <a href="/contact" class="page-cta-link">Or send us a message &rarr;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero h1 { color: var(--color-cream-d); }
  .page-hero .page-intro { color: rgba(247, 242, 231, 0.72); }

  .page-section { background: var(--color-white); }
  .prose-narrow {
    max-width: 680px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 20px;
  }
  .prose-narrow p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.78;
    color: var(--color-charcoal);
  }
  .prose-emphasis {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-style: italic;
    font-size: 1.15rem !important;
    color: var(--color-pine) !important;
  }
  .page-cta {
    margin-top: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 20px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .page-cta-link {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-pine);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--color-brass);
    padding-bottom: 2px;
  }
</style>
